,"tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-tolerance","tag-virtue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9XV","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":32083,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/khuluq-islam-al-haya\/","url_meta":{"origin":38311,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Islam is characterized by modesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, every religion has a character and the character of Islam is modesty.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4182 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32079,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/entire-deen-haya\/","url_meta":{"origin":38311,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Haya: All of Islam revolves around modesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Qurrah ibn Iyas reported: We were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when modesty was mentioned to him. They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is modesty part of the religion?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cRather, it is the entire religion.\u201d Then, the Prophet said, \u201cVerily, modesty,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17149,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/12\/haya-jamil-fashihah-ugly\/","url_meta":{"origin":38311,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Haya&#8217;: Modesty is beauty, obscenity is ugly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVulgarity is not found in anything but that it disgraces it, and modesty is not found in anything but that it beautifies it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1974 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11676,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/23\/haya-modesty-mind-body-soul\/","url_meta":{"origin":38311,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Be modest with Allah in mind, body, soul","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe modest before Allah, as is His right.\u201d We said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, surely we have modesty, all praise is due to Allah!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIt is not so. Rather, modesty before Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27047,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/01\/20\/most-haya-uthman\/","url_meta":{"origin":38311,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Uthman: Most modest of the Ummah is Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cModesty is part of faith, and the most modest of my nation is Uthman.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq li-Ibn 'Asa\u0304kir 39\/92 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40573,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/04\/men-need-permission\/","url_meta":{"origin":38311,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Modesty: Husband&#8217;s permission to enter women\u2019s homes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Amr ibn al-\u2018As reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited us from requesting entrance into the homes of women unless their husbands give permission. Source: Musnad Ah\u03